[
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": "老头儿",
    "listener": "char_zhang_chao_tang",
    "text": "什么匪帮？土匪有这么狠吗？那是官兵干的好事。",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 41,
    "line_end": 41
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": "老头儿",
    "listener": "char_zhang_chao_tang",
    "text": "你这位小相公看来是第一次出门，什么世情也不懂的了。长官？长官带头干呀，好的东西他先拿，好看的娘们他先要。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 43,
    "line_end": 43
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhang_chao_tang",
    "speaker_name": "张朝唐",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "官兵？官兵怎么会如此无法无天、奸淫掳掠？他们长官不理吗？",
    "tone": "激动",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 41,
    "line_end": 41
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yang_peng_ju",
    "speaker_name": "杨鹏举",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "在下武会镖局姓杨，路经贵地，并非保镖，没向各位当家投帖拜谒。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 201,
    "line_end": 201
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": "杨鹏举",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "杨大爷今日落在你们手中，要杀就杀，不必多说。",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 171,
    "line_end": 171
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": "孙仲寿",
    "listener": "char_zhang_chao_tang",
    "text": "张兄文笔不凡，武穆诸葛这两句话，荣宠九泉。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 297,
    "line_end": 297
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": "应松",
    "listener": "char_cui_qiu_shan",
    "text": "这位幼主名叫袁承志，由我们四人教他识字练武。他聪明得很，一教就会，但再跟着我们，练下去进境一定不大。",
    "tone": "恳求",
    "chapter": 2,
    "line_start": 57,
    "line_end": 57
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_cui_qiu_shan",
    "speaker_name": "崔秋山",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "承各位瞧得起，兄弟原不该推辞，不过兄弟现下是在闯将李大哥军中，来去无定，常跟官军接仗，也不知能活到那一天。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 2,
    "line_start": 61,
    "line_end": 61
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": "char_cui_qiu_shan",
    "text": "崔叔叔，你刚才抓住那两个坏人，使的是什么功夫？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 2,
    "line_start": 63,
    "line_end": 63
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_cui_qiu_shan",
    "speaker_name": "崔秋山",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "我所会的已全部传了给你，你要好好记住。日后是否有成，全凭你自己练习了。临敌时局面千变万化，七分靠功夫，三分靠机灵，一味蛮打，决难取胜。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 2,
    "line_start": 103,
    "line_end": 103
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": "char_cui_qiu_shan",
    "text": "崔叔叔，我跟你到李将军那里。",
    "tone": "恳求",
    "chapter": 2,
    "line_start": 105,
    "line_end": 105
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_an_da_niang",
    "speaker_name": "安大娘",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "承志，我一见你就很喜欢，就当你是我的亲儿子一般。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 9,
    "line_end": 9
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_mu_ren_qing",
    "speaker_name": "穆人清",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "你这娃儿，谁教你叫我师父的？你怎知我准肯收你为徒？",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 31,
    "line_end": 31
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_mu_ren_qing",
    "speaker_name": "穆人清",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "好吧，瞧你故世的父亲份上，就收了你吧！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 33,
    "line_end": 33
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_mu_ren_qing",
    "speaker_name": "穆人清",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "从今而后，你是我华山派的弟子了。我多年前收过两个徒弟，此后一直没再遇到聪颖肯学的孩子，这些年来没再传人。你是我的第三个弟子，也是我的关门徒弟。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 49,
    "line_end": 49
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_mu_ren_qing",
    "speaker_name": "穆人清",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "我姓穆，叫做穆人清，江湖上朋友叫我做神剑仙猿。你记着点，下次别让人家问住，你师父叫什么呀？",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 51,
    "line_end": 51
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_mu_ren_qing",
    "speaker_name": "穆人清",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "剑乃利器，以之行善，其善无穷，以之行恶，其恶亦无穷。今日我要你发个重誓，一生之中，决不可妄杀一个无辜之人。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 89,
    "line_end": 89
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_mu_sang_dao_ren",
    "speaker_name": "木桑道人",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "好好好，有其师必有其徒，师父不要脸，徒弟也没出息。",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 117,
    "line_end": 117
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": "温青",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "天下的财天下人发得，难道这金子是你的？",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 111,
    "line_end": 111
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "他们要抢你财物，既没抢去，也就罢了，何苦多伤性命？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 151,
    "line_end": 151
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": "温青",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "你没见他刚才的卑鄙恶毒么？要是我落入他手里，只怕还有更惨的呢。你别以为帮了我一次，就可随便教训人，我才不理呢。",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 153,
    "line_end": 153
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": "温青",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "袁大哥，适才幸得你出声示警，叫我避开暗器，谢谢你啦。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 153,
    "line_end": 153
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": "温青",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "不分青红皂白，便是爱做滥好人！到底你是帮我呢，还是帮这臭老头儿？",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 237,
    "line_end": 237
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我不要，你都拿去，我帮你并非为了金子。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 247,
    "line_end": 247
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": "温青",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "月白风清，这么好的夜晚。袁兄雅人，不怕辜负了大好时光吗？",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 3,
    "line_end": 3
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": "温青",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "我从来不吹给谁听。他们就知道动刀动剑，也不爱听这个。",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 25,
    "line_end": 25
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": "温青",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "因此上你永远不会再来了。我⋯⋯我再也见你不着了。",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 25,
    "line_end": 25
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你一定瞧得出，我什么也不懂。我初入江湖，没学会说谎。你说我心里瞧不起你，觉得你讨厌，老实说，那本来不错，我起初见你动不动杀人，很不以为然。不过现下有些不同了。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 27,
    "line_end": 27
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": "温青",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "我妈妈做姑娘的时候，受了人欺侮，生下我来。我五位爷爷打不过这人，后来约了许许多多好手，才把那人打跑，因此我是没爸爸的人，我是个私生⋯⋯",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 29,
    "line_end": 29
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "这可怪不得你，也怪不得你妈妈，是那坏人不好。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 31,
    "line_end": 31
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": "温青",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "我没亲哥哥，咱们结拜为兄弟，好不好？",
    "tone": "恳求",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 63,
    "line_end": 63
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": "温仪",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "他是我丈夫，虽然我们没拜天地，可是在我心中，他是我的亲丈夫。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 41,
    "line_end": 41
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": "温仪",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "棋仙派温氏兄弟听了：送上你们弟弟温方禄尸首一具，便请笑纳。此人当年污辱我亲姊之后，又将其杀害，并将我父母兄长，一家五口尽数杀死。我孤身一人逃脱在外，现归来报仇。血债十倍回报，方解我恨。",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 43,
    "line_end": 43
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": "温仪",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你为什么下我的毒？",
    "tone": "恐惧",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 161,
    "line_end": 161
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": "温仪",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "十九年来，我没跟爹爹说过一句话，以后我也永不会跟他说话。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 169,
    "line_end": 169
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": "温仪",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "他有没有遗书？有没提到我？",
    "tone": "恳求",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 261,
    "line_end": 261
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": "温仪",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "他没怪我，他心里仍记着我，想着我⋯⋯而今我要去了，要去见他了⋯⋯",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 267,
    "line_end": 267
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": "温仪",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "我⋯⋯我世上亲人，只有⋯⋯只有这个女儿，请你⋯⋯一生一世⋯⋯照看着她⋯⋯",
    "tone": "恳求",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 269,
    "line_end": 269
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": "黄真",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "恭喜发财！掌柜的宝号是什么字号？大老板一向做什么生意？",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 9,
    "line_end": 9
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": "黄真",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "这批金子倘使是兄弟自己的，虽然现今世界不太平，赚钱不大容易，不过朋友们当真要使，拿去也没关系。须知胜败乃兵家常事，赚蚀乃商家常事。",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 61,
    "line_end": 61
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": "黄真",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "我那有这么大的才学？这是闯王手下大将李岩李公子作的歌儿。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 243,
    "line_end": 243
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": "黄真",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "袁师弟，你实在一点也不懂生意经。奇货可居，怎不起价？",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 183,
    "line_end": 183
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": "青青",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "那就叫做青梅竹马了。",
    "tone": "嘲讽",
    "chapter": 8,
    "line_start": 5,
    "line_end": 5
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我生病也是假的呀，你别当真！",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 8,
    "line_start": 47,
    "line_end": 47
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": "焦公礼",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "这位恩公姓夏，外号叫做金蛇郎君。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 8,
    "line_start": 315,
    "line_end": 315
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "金蛇郎君不能来了，由他公子和兄弟前来，给各位做个和事老。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 9,
    "line_start": 5,
    "line_end": 5
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": "孙仲君",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "什么金蛇铁蛇，快给我下去，别在这里碍手碍脚。",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 9,
    "line_start": 17,
    "line_end": 17
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "久闻仙都派位居四大剑派，剑法精微奥妙，今日正好见识领教。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 9,
    "line_start": 47,
    "line_end": 47
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": "梅剑和",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "你叫什么名字？谁叫你到这里来多事？",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 9,
    "line_start": 11,
    "line_end": 11
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": "归二娘",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "要知学无止境，天外有天，人上有人。学了点功夫，就随便欺侮人。",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 9,
    "line_start": 335,
    "line_end": 335
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "寨主你也辛苦。兄弟赶道倒没什么，就是行李笨重，金银珠宝太多，带着讨厌。",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 10,
    "line_start": 239,
    "line_end": 239
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": "沙天广",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "袁相公在家纳福，岂不是好，何必出门奔波？要知江湖上险恶得很呢。",
    "tone": "嘲讽",
    "chapter": 10,
    "line_start": 243,
    "line_end": 243
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": "阿九",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你老人家说，咱们闲着也是闲着，不如到山东逛逛，乘便就瞧瞧货样。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 10,
    "line_start": 265,
    "line_end": 265
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你们打了半天，又在我箱上写什么甲乙丙丁，山东直隶，现下玩够了吧？哈哈，我可要擦去啦！",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 10,
    "line_start": 389,
    "line_end": 389
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": "阿九",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "你这人呆头呆脑的，还是乖乖的也赶快回家吧，别把性命在道上送了。",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 10,
    "line_start": 381,
    "line_end": 381
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "speaker_name": "青青",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "他们伤了这许多人，只在铁箱外面摸得几下，你说是赚了还是蚀了，得请你大师哥用铁算盘来算一下了。",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 3,
    "line_end": 3
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "帮强盗，杀官兵！你在这里守住！",
    "tone": "激动",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 17,
    "line_end": 17
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_cui_qiu_shan",
    "speaker_name": "褚红柳",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "他们以为一下子就把咱们尽数杀了，只须给咱们安上几个什么王、什么星的厉害匪号，奏报上去，岂不是大功一件？",
    "tone": "嘲讽",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 29,
    "line_end": 29
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "官逼民反，今日可教我亲身遇上了。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 29,
    "line_end": 29
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_sun_zhong_shou",
    "speaker_name": "孙仲寿",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "公子，这里又有盗帮，又有投降的大批官兵，他们对你都很敬服，正是难遇的良机。何不暂缓赴京，把这批人手好好整顿一下。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 89,
    "line_end": 89
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_cheng_qing_zhu",
    "speaker_name": "程青竹",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "多谢公子，在下得知公子是袁督师的骨肉，实是欢喜之极。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 95,
    "line_end": 95
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "昏君奸臣为非作歹，那也罢了，北京城的老百姓，却也如此可恶！",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 127,
    "line_end": 127
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_sha_tian_guang",
    "speaker_name": "沙天广",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "兄弟心里，也有一位年轻的英雄，只怕不见得比焦帮主所说的那位差了。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 169,
    "line_end": 169
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "兄弟年轻识浅，今日得能参与泰山大会，已感荣幸，只盼追随各位前辈之后，稍效微劳，岂敢担当大任？还请别选贤能。",
    "tone": "恳求",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 183,
    "line_end": 183
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_sun_zhong_shou",
    "speaker_name": "孙仲寿",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "公子，你谦辞不就，倘若盟主一席不幸落入奸人之手，祸害不小。你如能领袖群雄，谋干大事，督师的血海深仇就可得报。督师一生做事，向来就是当仁不让，不避艰危。",
    "tone": "恳求",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 199,
    "line_end": 199
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": "char_gui_xin_shu",
    "text": "二师哥，请你把孟老爷子的穴道解开了。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 12,
    "line_start": 177,
    "line_end": 177
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gui_er_niang",
    "speaker_name": "归二娘",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "师弟，我们夫妇真是感激不尽。",
    "tone": "感激",
    "chapter": 12,
    "line_start": 193,
    "line_end": 193
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gui_xin_shu",
    "speaker_name": "归辛树",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "师弟，你很好，很好。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 12,
    "line_start": 193,
    "line_end": 193
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gui_xin_shu",
    "speaker_name": "归辛树",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "师弟，自今而后，你便如我的亲兄弟一般！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 12,
    "line_start": 213,
    "line_end": 213
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_he_tie_shou",
    "speaker_name": "何铁手",
    "listener": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "text": "那么把他公子留下来，先祭了先父再说。",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 15,
    "line_start": 169,
    "line_end": 169
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "speaker_name": "青青",
    "listener": "char_he_tie_shou",
    "text": "金蛇郎君是我爹爹，你们问他干么？",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 15,
    "line_start": 149,
    "line_end": 149
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_he_hong_yao",
    "speaker_name": "何红药",
    "listener": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "text": "他居然没死，还留下了你这孽种！我是何红药，他在那里？",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 15,
    "line_start": 151,
    "line_end": 151
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_he_tie_shou",
    "speaker_name": "何铁手",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "袁相公模样斯文，却原来身负绝技，让我领教几招。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 15,
    "line_start": 163,
    "line_end": 163
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_he_tie_shou",
    "speaker_name": "何铁手",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "他跟敝教很有渊源，家父就是因他而归天的。敝教教众万余人，没一个不想找他。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 15,
    "line_start": 167,
    "line_end": 167
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_he_tie_shou",
    "speaker_name": "何铁手",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "袁相公倘若不嫌小妹资质愚鲁，就请收归门下。",
    "tone": "恳求",
    "chapter": 16,
    "line_start": 223,
    "line_end": 223
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_jiao_wan_er",
    "speaker_name": "焦宛儿",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "闵叔叔，侄女错怪好人，冒犯你老人家啦。",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 16,
    "line_start": 75,
    "line_end": 75
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_shui_yun",
    "speaker_name": "水云道人",
    "listener": "char_jiao_wan_er",
    "text": "这戒杀刀是自杀用的，要是仙都弟子遇敌之时，武功不如，而对方又苦苦相逼，脱身不得，便须以此匕首自杀，免损仙都威名。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 16,
    "line_start": 69,
    "line_end": 69
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_li_yan",
    "speaker_name": "李岩",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "兄弟，闯王大业告成之后，我和你隐居山林，饮酒为乐，今后的日子长着呢。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 13,
    "line_start": 67,
    "line_end": 67
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": "char_li_yan",
    "text": "若能如此，实慰生平之愿。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 13,
    "line_start": 67,
    "line_end": 67
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": "char_chong_zhen_huang_di",
    "text": "我是前蓟辽督师袁公的儿子，名叫袁承志。你鞑子侵犯我大明江山，我千万汉人，恨不得食你之肉。我今日来行刺，是为我爹爹报仇，为我成千成万死在你手下的汉人报仇。",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 14,
    "line_start": 29,
    "line_end": 29
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_tai_ji",
    "speaker_name": "皇太极",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "南朝所以流寇四起，说来说去，也只一个道理，就是老百姓没饭吃。咱们得了南朝江山，第一件大事，就是要让天下百姓人人有饭吃⋯⋯",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 13,
    "line_start": 227,
    "line_end": 227
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": "char_yu_zhen_zi",
    "text": "你是汉人，怎地反帮鞑子？",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 14,
    "line_start": 7,
    "line_end": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yu_zhen_zi",
    "speaker_name": "玉真子",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "倔强小子，死到临头，还在胡说。",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 14,
    "line_start": 7,
    "line_end": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_tai_ji",
    "speaker_name": "皇太极",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "你爹爹袁公，我是很佩服的。可惜崇祯皇帝不明是非，杀害了忠良。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 14,
    "line_start": 35,
    "line_end": 35
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": "char_huang_tai_ji",
    "text": "快将我杀了，不用你假惺惺。",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 14,
    "line_start": 33,
    "line_end": 33
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zu_da_shou",
    "speaker_name": "祖大寿",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "袁公子，你⋯⋯你长得这么大了，你⋯⋯你三岁的时候，我⋯⋯我抱过你的。",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 14,
    "line_start": 47,
    "line_end": 47
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zu_da_shou",
    "speaker_name": "祖大寿",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "你是袁督师的亲骨血，祖大寿身受督师厚恩，无以为报。",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 14,
    "line_start": 61,
    "line_end": 61
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zu_da_shou",
    "speaker_name": "祖大寿",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "袁督师忠义包天，他的公子怎能如我这般无耻，投降鞑子？",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 14,
    "line_start": 75,
    "line_end": 75
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zu_da_shou",
    "speaker_name": "祖大寿",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "多谢你叫我两声叔叔！",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 14,
    "line_start": 77,
    "line_end": 77
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_a_jiu",
    "speaker_name": "阿九",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "你别叫我殿下，我也不叫你袁相公。你初次识得我时，我是阿九，那么我永远就是阿九。",
    "tone": "恳求",
    "chapter": 17,
    "line_start": 321,
    "line_end": 321
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_a_jiu",
    "speaker_name": "阿九",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "只要你不忘了我，我⋯⋯我总是⋯⋯跟你在一起⋯⋯咱们将来⋯⋯还有这样的时候。",
    "tone": "恳求",
    "chapter": 18,
    "line_start": 43,
    "line_end": 43
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": "char_a_jiu",
    "text": "当然，永远不忘记你！",
    "tone": "激动",
    "chapter": 18,
    "line_start": 49,
    "line_end": 49
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_chong_zhen_huang_di",
    "speaker_name": "崇祯",
    "listener": "char_a_jiu",
    "text": "孩儿，你为什么生在我家里⋯⋯",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 18,
    "line_start": 317,
    "line_end": 317
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你这狠心毒辣的昏君，竟什么人都杀，既害我父亲，又杀你自己女儿。我今日取你性命！",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 18,
    "line_start": 325,
    "line_end": 325
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_a_jiu",
    "speaker_name": "阿九",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "别杀我父皇，求你⋯⋯",
    "tone": "恳求",
    "chapter": 18,
    "line_start": 327,
    "line_end": 327
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": "char_chong_zhen_huang_di",
    "text": "我姓袁，是故兵部尚书、蓟辽督师袁崇焕之子！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 18,
    "line_start": 121,
    "line_end": 121
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_chong_zhen_huang_di",
    "speaker_name": "崇祯",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "现今我也颇为后悔了。",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 18,
    "line_start": 121,
    "line_end": 121
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": "char_chong_zhen_huang_di",
    "text": "我是为了国家而救你，要什么赏赐？嗯，是了，皇上既已后悔，求皇上下诏，洗雪先父的大冤。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 18,
    "line_start": 125,
    "line_end": 125
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_a_jiu",
    "speaker_name": "阿九",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "你放心，我永永远远，决不负你。",
    "tone": "恳求",
    "chapter": 18,
    "line_start": 137,
    "line_end": 137
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": "char_a_jiu",
    "text": "天下将有大变，身居深宫，不如远涉江湖，你要记得我这句话。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 18,
    "line_start": 137,
    "line_end": 137
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_a_jiu",
    "speaker_name": "阿九",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "不错，我宁愿随你在江湖上四处为家，远胜在宫里享福。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 18,
    "line_start": 139,
    "line_end": 139
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_li_zi_cheng",
    "speaker_name": "李自成",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "众将官兵士听着，入城之后，有人妄自杀伤百姓、奸淫掳掠的，一概斩首，决不宽容！",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 19,
    "line_start": 21,
    "line_end": 21
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_li_zi_cheng",
    "speaker_name": "李自成",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "你是承父之志，此后要助我抗御满洲鞑子入侵。我是承天！",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 19,
    "line_start": 25,
    "line_end": 25
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_li_zi_cheng",
    "speaker_name": "李自成",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我本是好好的百姓，给贪官污吏这一顿打，才忍无可忍，起来造反。哼，你父子俩假仁假义，说什么爱惜百姓。我军中上上下下，那一个不吃过你们的苦头？",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 19,
    "line_start": 47,
    "line_end": 47
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_li_zi_cheng",
    "speaker_name": "李自成",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "大伙儿这就散了罢，辛苦了这么久，也该过几天好日子了。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 19,
    "line_start": 209,
    "line_end": 209
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": "char_li_yan",
    "text": "大哥，你说闯王为民伸冤，为⋯⋯为百姓出气，就是这样么？",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 19,
    "line_start": 125,
    "line_end": 125
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_liu_zong_min",
    "speaker_name": "刘宗敏",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "这天下是大王的天下，是我们老兄弟出死入生、从刀山枪林里打出来的天下。我们会打江山，难道不会坐江山么？",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 19,
    "line_start": 89,
    "line_end": 89
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_li_yan",
    "speaker_name": "李岩",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "大王虽已有疑我之意，但为臣尽忠，为友尽义，我和大王共历患难，创建大业，终不能眼见大王大业败坏，闭口不言。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 19,
    "line_start": 247,
    "line_end": 247
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_he_hong_yao",
    "speaker_name": "何红药",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "雪宜，你出来！你想不想见我啊？",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 19,
    "line_start": 415,
    "line_end": 415
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_he_hong_yao",
    "speaker_name": "何红药",
    "listener": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "text": "你出去吧，我饶了你啦！",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 19,
    "line_start": 423,
    "line_end": 423
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_he_hong_yao",
    "speaker_name": "何红药",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "夏郎，夏郎，我来瞧你啦！",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 19,
    "line_start": 431,
    "line_end": 431
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "speaker_name": "青青",
    "listener": "char_he_hong_yao",
    "text": "她跟我爹爹、妈妈同葬一穴，她如死后有知，心中也必欢喜。但盼他们三人不要吵架才好。",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 19,
    "line_start": 471,
    "line_end": 471
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "speaker_name": "青青",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "既有金枝玉叶，当然抛了我平民百姓。",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 19,
    "line_start": 277,
    "line_end": 277
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "speaker_name": "青青",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "你答应了我妈⋯⋯要⋯⋯要一生⋯⋯一世照应我的⋯⋯你骗了我⋯⋯又⋯⋯又⋯⋯骗我妈⋯⋯",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 20,
    "line_start": 217,
    "line_end": 217
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "text": "我不骗你，我自然一生一世照应你！",
    "tone": "恳求",
    "chapter": 20,
    "line_start": 217,
    "line_end": 217
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": "char_yu_zhen_zi",
    "text": "你此刻倒已穿上了衣衫，咱们好好的来打一架。",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 20,
    "line_start": 231,
    "line_end": 231
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_a_jiu",
    "speaker_name": "阿九",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "承志哥哥，我要跟师父到藏边去学功夫，千里迢迢，不大容易相见了。我等你⋯⋯等你⋯⋯三年。你三年不来，就不必来了。我就落发做了尼姑⋯⋯心里永远⋯⋯永远记着你⋯⋯不，我等你十年⋯⋯",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 20,
    "line_start": 331,
    "line_end": 331
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": "char_a_jiu",
    "text": "我一定会来见你。阿九妹子，不到一年，我就来啦！我见不到你，我会死的。",
    "tone": "激动",
    "chapter": 20,
    "line_start": 331,
    "line_end": 331
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_mu_ren_qing",
    "speaker_name": "穆人清",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我年事已高，不能再理世事俗务。华山派门户事宜，从今日起由大弟子黄真执掌。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 20,
    "line_start": 313,
    "line_end": 313
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "speaker_name": "青青",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "刚才你跌倒，为什么跌在她面前，却不跌在我面前？要是你摔在我面前，我也会不顾自己性命，扑在你身上救你。",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 20,
    "line_start": 317,
    "line_end": 317
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "speaker_name": "青青",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "以后你心中就只有她，我宁可死了！",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 20,
    "line_start": 319,
    "line_end": 319
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_he_tie_shou",
    "speaker_name": "何惕守",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "师父，你只要不娶夏姑娘，她做不成我师娘，这一生就不能管你，她再跳崖投海，都不跟你相干。阿九姑娘永永远远在等你。",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 20,
    "line_start": 339,
    "line_end": 339
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_he_tie_shou",
    "speaker_name": "何惕守",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "男人如不把我爱得要死要活，发疯发癫，嫁了他有什么味道？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 20,
    "line_start": 455,
    "line_end": 455
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_li_yan",
    "speaker_name": "李岩",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "人生数十年，宛如春梦一场。",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 20,
    "line_start": 403,
    "line_end": 403
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_li_yan",
    "speaker_name": "李岩",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "我跟你有情有义，做皇帝可享有普天下的财宝美女，我岂能为了做皇帝，舍了我们兄弟的情义。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 20,
    "line_start": 417,
    "line_end": 417
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": "char_li_yan",
    "text": "大哥，要是你做了皇帝，你就要杀我？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 20,
    "line_start": 417,
    "line_end": 417
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_li_yan",
    "speaker_name": "李岩",
    "listener": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "text": "决计不会！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 20,
    "line_start": 417,
    "line_end": 417
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "袁承志",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "师父常告诫，修习武功，须防走火入魔，一旦入魔，精神纷乱，不易收拾。金蛇郎君想到这里，已近乎走火入魔，我可不能跟着学了。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 37,
    "line_end": 37
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_an_da_niang",
    "speaker_name": "安大娘",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我也舍不得你啊。我要哑伯伯带你到一个人那里。他曾教过你崔叔叔武功。你崔叔叔只跟他学了两个月武艺，就这般了得。这位老前辈的武功天下无双，我要你去跟他学。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 9,
    "line_end": 9
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_an_da_niang",
    "speaker_name": "安大娘",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "承志，我一见你就很喜欢，就当你是我的亲儿子一般。今日你不顾性命的相救小慧，我更加永远忘不了你。今晚我要到一个很远的地方去。你跟着哑伯伯去。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 9,
    "line_end": 9
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_cao_hua_chun",
    "speaker_name": "曹化淳",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我们皇上的性子，真是固执得要命。我进言了好几次，皇上总说借兵灭寇，后患太多，只求两国议和罢兵，等大明灭了流寇，重重酬谢睿王爷。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 17,
    "line_start": 9,
    "line_end": 9
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_cui_qiu_shan",
    "speaker_name": "崔秋山",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "哼，开玩笑！你们两个鬼鬼祟祟在客店里商量，要混进山宗来，又说已禀告了曹太监，要派兵来一网打尽，这些话都给我听见啦！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 2,
    "line_start": 7,
    "line_end": 7
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_xia_qing_qing",
    "speaker_name": "夏青青",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "道长教了我一套功夫。这功夫啊，可真妙啦。别人向你拳打脚踢，你却只管跟他捉迷藏，东一溜，西一晃，他再也别想打到你。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 10,
    "line_start": 5,
    "line_end": 5
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_sun_zhong_shou",
    "speaker_name": "孙仲寿",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我们王将军知道袁督师在关外打鞑子，立了大功，很是佩服。袁督师为昏君冤枉害死，天下老百姓都气愤得很。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 321,
    "line_end": 321
  }
]
